name: Rope Dog Leash: Sea Foam
description:
All leashes are made from locally sourced materials from Portland, Oregon.

- Hand made & hand dyed cotton rope leash
-Cotton blend leash whipped with waxed hemp string
- Made from 1/4" rope, measures approximately 50" long
- Silver metal swivel clip
- Please note that some color & length variation may occur

All leashes are made with the traditional eye splice loop commonly used by sailors. The rope ends are spliced then whipped for a durable and seamless finish.


**We are not responsible for any injuries caused as a result of improper leash use.**
